Java : Servlets and JSP

Spring MVC
Spring Boot Framework

	FrameWork
	
MVC Architecture : Model View Controller

	View : HTML , CSS , Javascript , Bootstrap .....
	Model : Database and Business Logics
	Controller : Request and Response	
	
	Controller >> Model >> Controller >> View >> Response View
	
MVC-2 Architecture : Model View Controller

	View : HTML , CSS , Javascript , Bootstrap .....
	Model : 
		Database 		 : Model
		Business Logics : Service
	Controller : Request and Response	
	
	Controller >> Service >> Model >> Service >> Controller >> View >> Response View	
	
	
	Controller Layer
	Service Layer
	Database Layer
	View Layer
	
